      "text": "<p><code>animation-duration</code> svojstvo za zvezdu sa klasom <code>star-1</code> treba da ostane 1s.</p>",
      "testString": "const starOne = document.querySelector('.star-1');\nconst starOneStyle = window.getComputedStyle(starOne); \nassert.equal(starOneStyle?.animationDuration, '1s');"
